Room to Improve - Series 9, Programme 5




Revisits

Dermot Bannon concludes series 9 with three of his favourite properties from earlier shows. He is reunited with pub owners in Longford whom he persuaded to make use of empty space, a couple who moved from California to Bishoptown and a semi-detached home in Malahide designed to be completely wheelchair-accessible.




Original Air Date: 06-Mar-2016
